# 2022 CS Warsaw Cup

Kévin Aymoz
| championwomen =  Ekaterina Kurakova
| championpairs =  Anastasia Golubeva / Hektor Giotopoulos Moore
| championdance =  Loïcia Demougeot / Théo le Mercier
| previouscomp = 2021 CS Warsaw Cup
| nextcomp = 2023 CS Warsaw Cup
| previouscs = 2022 CS Ice Challenge
| nextcs = 2022 CS Golden Spin of Zagreb
}}
The 2022 CS Warsaw Cup was held on November 17–20, 2022, in Warsaw, Poland. It was the ninth event of the 2022–23 ISU Challenger Series. Medals were awarded in men's singles, women's singles, pair skating, and ice dance.
Entries
The International Skating Union published the full list of entries on October 26, 2022.
